    book donations from our community.
    <strong>
        (If you want to know more about Imbala, a member-run cooperative, visit the <a href="/en/about-us">about page</a>!)
    </strong>
</p>
<p>
    Please take down a book! <strong>Read it here</strong>, and when you are
    done, put it back where it was (use the colors)!
</p>
<p>
    The <strong>legend </strong>is:
<ul>
<li><span class="color-name azure">Light blue</span> - The Nakba and the Occupation</li>
<li><span class="color-name blue">Dark blue</span> - Other local struggles in Palestine / Israel</li>
