<li><span class="color-name green">Green</span> - Fiction and non-fiction</li>
<li><span class="color-name">White</span> - Not for checkout</li>
</ul>    

<p>
    Don’t forget to look at the <strong>fanzines </strong>in the crates on the
    bottom shelf. If you have a fanzine you want to leave here, place it in the
    collection and send us an email so we can add it to the catalog.
</p>
